{"tid":999894,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"十年後撞到ex","createTime":"2019-01-29T05:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T04:42:50.000Z","uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"058b2f1aecb8a37fe25c192dec5a4b8298ad2dd6","tid":999894,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜喺街撞返以前嘅ex<br />\n果個大大話話都已經係10年前嘅初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當年我都算係學校入面嘅校花<br />\n佢都追左我好耐先追到我<br />\n我地一齊果段日子都幾青春 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以見返佢我個心都依然係會有心跳嘅感覺<br />\n本身重諗住撞返佢<br />\n可以keep返contact<br />\n就算唔可以再續情緣<br />\n都希望可以做返朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知一見到我第一句竟然係話<br />\n&ldquo;嘩!! 10年無見,估唔到你變左咁多,由女神變肥豬扒&rdquo;<br />\n果下我個心好似比刀拮左一下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗返其實佢都講得無錯嘅<br />\n見到佢10年黎都依然係咁charm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反我就走哂樣<br />\n抵比人咁話<br />\n利申:真絲非假膠"},{"pid":"57da02c081b9bfc48d3f51f29de744fa84cc95c5","tid":999894,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">GAY</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc5e7f27282bc0e823ba5f5743a3c98efbf26113","tid":999894,"uid":50658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b901ebbfb55df2a46b97a32292346e988a91723","tid":999894,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"57da02c081b9bfc48d3f51f29de744fa84cc95c5","tid":999894,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">GAY</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:14:03.000Z","msg":"絲非膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227308e7c425a58d8028c90e5ac4de0a401c2643","tid":999894,"uid":186323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:14:18.000Z","msg":"點走樣法？ 肥咗好撚多？"},{"pid":"2c34bb8018470f6f08c5b6e1f2006837754eaf01","tid":999894,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1908a3939396ab85e34ad8ee0472677ddb257e9c","tid":999894,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"227308e7c425a58d8028c90e5ac4de0a401c2643","tid":999894,"uid":186323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:14:18.000Z","msg":"點走樣法？ 肥咗好撚多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"老咗殘咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b413444634a00141570b9edb4258124affaadd","tid":999894,"uid":89958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"樓主有多重人格"},{"pid":"658c5ddf12d6482c49d452327f3b492c68923cc6","tid":999894,"uid":47857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:16:13.000Z","msg":"fun<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">GAY</span></span>ing"},{"pid":"83f2b20089f5491136c1d7e2554a96ac1e31ffb4","tid":999894,"uid":161126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:18:39.000Z","msg":"試過啦 點頭互相寒暄左一陣就走"},{"pid":"5325dcd9a68d9a98f82caadf67079fdcc4c2f576","tid":999894,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f2b20089f5491136c1d7e2554a96ac1e31ffb4","tid":999894,"uid":161126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:18:39.000Z","msg":"試過啦 點頭互相寒暄左一陣就走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:24:34.000Z","msg":"如果知道結果係咁<br />\n我都會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d96643fa7b9a2ac1e5f3d549f0708d201fd1df","tid":999894,"uid":196627,"like"